body:
## What happened

I was editing some text while the flutter app was in the background,
Then after saving returned to the flutter app

## Version information

Android Studio `3.2.1` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 30.0.1` • Dart plugin `181.5656`

Flutter 0.10.2 • channel beta • https://github.com/flutter/flutter.git
Framework • revision d8cbb80206 (2 weeks ago) • 2018-10-26 01:30:21 -0400
Engine • revision 6c2ade9fa2
Tools • Dart 2.1.0-dev.8.0.flutter-bf26f760b1

## Exception

java.io.IOException: error from app.callServiceExtension: "Bad state: No element"

comment_data.body: The root cause of this problem is an error thrown by the Dart code in the flutter tool. Without more information there isn't much we can do. See #2657 for more detail.
